ur Interacthon! Talk\, Connect\, Practice English A marathon of interactive recreational\, social and informational activities for newcomers and community members! What's in it for you? Try new activities [ŌĆ”] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Fri		\n		\n			27		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		The Psychology of Love	\n\n					\n		\n		March 27 @ 3:00 pm - 5:00 pm	\n	\n					\n	\n		Parkdale Library	\n	\n		1303 Queen Street West\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	What is happening in our brain when we fall in love? Come learn the science behind it all! For more information\, please get in touch with Daniella at DDjaigbe@culturelink.ca or [ŌĆ”] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Fri		\n		\n			27		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		Finding Home Through Art	\n\n					\n		\n		March 27 @ 4:00 pm - 5:00 pm	\n	\n					\n	\n		CultureLink	\n	\n		2340 Dundas St W\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n					\n\n	\n					\n				Adults	\n\n				\n\n				\n	Join us for a relaxing afternoon of collage-making to reflect on your journey to Canada. Refreshments will be provided FREE TTC tickets for eligible participants For more information\, contact Charlotte [ŌĆ”] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Tue		\n		\n			31		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		Youth Connect Hub	\n\n					\n		\n		March 31 @ 3:30 pm - 5:30 pm	\n	\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		Youth Connect Hub\n	\n\n\n					\n	\n		CultureLink Children & Youth Centre	\n	\n		3535 Dundas Street West\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	A safe and welcoming space for youth to connect\, relax\, and have fun. Enjoy group games\, creative activities\, food sessions\, and conversations that support emotional well-being and confidence. For Newcomer [ŌĆ”] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n	\n		\n			April 2026		\n	\n\n\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Tue		\n		\n			14		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		Youth Connect Hub	\n\n					\n		\n		April 14 @ 3:30 pm - 5:30 pm	\n	\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		Youth Connect Hub\n	\n\n\n					\n	\n		CultureLink Children & Youth Centre	\n	\n		3535 Dundas Street West\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	A safe and welcoming space for youth to connect\, relax\, and have fun. Enjoy group games\, creative activities\, food sessions\, and conversations that support emotional well-being and confidence. For Newcomer [ŌĆ”] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n			\n		\n\n		\n	\n		\n	\n		\n	\n\n		\n			Previous Events		\n	\n\n\n		\n	\n		Today	\n\n\n		\n	\n		\n			Next Events		\n		\n	\n\n	\n\n	\n\n\n		\n	\n		\n			\n				Subscribe to calendar			\n			\n	\n\n		\n		\n			\n									\n\n	\n		Google Calendar	\n\n									\n\n	\n		iCalendar	\n\n									\n\n	\n		Outlook 365	\n\n									\n\n	\n		Outlook Live	\n\n									\n\n	\n		Export .ics file	\n\n									\n\n	\n		Export Outlook .ics file
